mobisocial.musubi.webapp

Class WebAppActivity

  • java.lang.Object
    • Activity
      • android.support.v4.app.FragmentActivity
        • mobisocial.musubi.ui.MusubiBaseActivity
          • mobisocial.musubi.webapp.WebAppActivity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SupportActivity, SherlockActivity, InstrumentedActivity
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SketchWrapperActivity

    public class WebAppActivity
extends MusubiBaseActivity
    Runs a webapp by injecting SocialKit-JS in a webview. SocialKitJS is bound to the application given in the extra EXTRA_APP_ID, which must be set by Musubi in a trusted way-- this activity cannot be safely exported. AppObj
